data.description: Country Living minutes from Parker!* 6.4 acres of prime Horse Property with Panoramic Mountain Views, 3-car garage and Walk-out Bsmt, Deck, Patio & Large Barn/5 Stalls* Huge, Updated 3893 SqFt with 5 bedroom/4 full baths. Formal Living/Dining, Great Room, Family Room, Game Room, Gourmet Kitchen, Eat-in/Dining Nook, 2 Gas log Fireplaces, Vaults/Hi-Volume Ceilings* Open & Bright-lots of natural light. Bright Open kitchen with Pantry, Kitchen Island, Spacious Counters and lots of Cabinets* Primary Bedroom Retreat with Fireplace, Private EnSuite 5-piece bath* Fully finished Walk-out Basement with Family room, 4th bedroom, Game room/office/bonus room* 5 stall barn with tack room, loft and extra space, electricity, 3 water spigots, 5 12x12 stalls 30 amp plug for RV hookup* 3-car garage* Fully fenced + Pasture fenced* Newer roof, ext paint, furnace and A/C* LOW LOW HOA & Taxes: Parker address yet Elbert County taxes! Community of Equestrian properties near schools, parks, shops, restaurants, trails, Colorado Horse Park* Near E-470, 30 min to DIA, 20 to DTC*
